{"tid":746906,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"SKYTRAX 2018全球最佳航空公司排行出爐！因航再跌一位排第六","createTime":"2018-07-18T03:17:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T18:31:32.000Z","uid":58958,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"16e7a1fa44a26e7a55d79be789fe85888f61bb8d","tid":746906,"uid":58958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T03:17:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/211995/skytrax-2018全球最佳航空公司排行出爐-國泰再跌一位排第六\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F211995%2Fskytrax-2018%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%B3%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%8E%92%E8%A1%8C%E5%87%BA%E7%88%90-%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B0%E5%86%8D%E8%B7%8C%E4%B8%80%E4%BD%8D%E6%8E%92%E7%AC%AC%E5%85%AD&d=t%2FClPAMlwCBvXe8NzHokiqEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=490ec968\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/211995/skytrax-2018全球最佳航空公司排行出爐-國泰再跌一位排第六</a><br />\n<br />\n英國航空服務權威調查機構「SKYTRAX」公布2018全球最佳航空公司排名，首位由Singapore Airlines航空奪得，至於以本港為基地的<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因航</span></span>排名則較去年下跌一位，排第六。而香港航空則擠身二十大。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/111348_78aa97f2e71065123d9b1292d86aad60.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F111348_78aa97f2e71065123d9b1292d86aad60.png&h=2986267e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSKYTRAX公布今年「全球十大最佳航空公司」排名，國泰再跌一位，排第六。（資料圖片／李澤彤攝）<br />\n<br />\n國泰排名再跌　被長榮超越<br />\n<br />\n被喻為「航空界奧斯卡」的SKYTRAX公布今年「全球最佳航空公司」。曾於2014年奪冠、以香港為基地的國泰航空名繼續下跌至第6，較去年下跌一位，取而代之的是台灣的長榮航空，由去年的第6升至今年的第5，為兩岸三地之中排名最高的航空公司。<br />\n<br />\n至於去年屈居第二的新加圾航空就晉身榜首，第二名為卡塔爾航空、第三名則是ANA全日空。今年新打入10大的是泰國國際航空。<br />\n<br />\n港航打入二十大　南航排名躍升<br />\n<br />\n雖然國泰排名再跌，但仍有本港航空公司排名有進步，例如香港航空的排名，由去年的24位升至20位，首次打入20大；至於港龍則由27位微升一級至26位。<br />\n<br />\n另外，部分內地航空公司排名亦上升，其中海南航空由去年的第9升至今年的第8；國營的南方航空由去年的23位，升至今年的14位。<br />\n<br />\n是次調查由2017年8月至2018年5月進行，由來自100個國藉、2,036名乘客參加調查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/111639_c342d8b95c6dea0cdb3f5b560055a55b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F111639_c342d8b95c6dea0cdb3f5b560055a55b.png&h=3a1da9e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n資料來源： SKYTRAX"},{"pid":"74be35531cdc92ee7d25f43dfbe602d5b92620a8","tid":746906,"uid":17866,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T03:50:37.000Z","msg":"因航唔搵番個鬼佬ceo等收皮啦<br />\n貴又唔夠當地龍頭平同靚<br />\n位又改窄，空姐又老又醜又惡，態度極差<br />\n平又唔夠腥港航空平，人地空姐係廢但起埋有個樣睇下<br />\n公司trip實用惡曬航空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想叫佢轉星航<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4cfae9021329495fb58b05ddfc42385f9965cc8","tid":746906,"uid":58958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74be35531cdc92ee7d25f43dfbe602d5b92620a8","tid":746906,"uid":17866,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T03:50:37.000Z","msg":"因航唔搵番個鬼佬ceo等收皮啦<br />\n貴又唔夠當地龍頭平同靚<br />\n位又改窄，空姐又老又醜又惡，態度極差<br />\n平又唔夠腥港航空平，人地空姐係廢但起埋有個樣睇下<br />\n公司trip實用惡曬航空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想叫佢轉星航<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T04:18:07.000Z","msg":"改名海南航空啦其實應該<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1407617b5d0dcab0dd5ecebbbd8469d589242de2","tid":746906,"uid":80332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T06:42:35.000Z","msg":"海航咁勁架原來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f357160fc4f2c50a375af04ea9aca97d432f3b3","tid":746906,"uid":5637,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T14:54:00.000Z","msg":"今年cut cost畀唔夠錢所以得第六<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid